comments: NYK commits a twenty-four second shot clock violation.
Robinson (NYK) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Curry (GSW) and absorbs the oncoming contact to his body prior to making any leg-to-leg contact.
Wiggins (GSW) makes legal contact with Robinson's (NYK) right hand that is a part of the ball and dislodges the ball during his shot attempt near the rim.
Fournier (NYK) moves into Kuminga's (GSW) path and makes contact to his body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Kuminga (GSW) makes contact to Burks' (NYK) arm that affects his shot attempt at the rim,
Curry (GSW) makes contact with the ball but does not dislodge the ball.  Burks (NYK) returns to the floor and a jump ball should be whistled instead of a traveling violation.
Burks (NYK) moves alongside Curry (GSW) on the driving shot attempt, and marginal body contact occurs.
Kuminga (GSW) touches the shot attempt by Randle (NYK) after it has reached its apex and is on the way down.  After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor is confirmed.
Curry (GSW) initiates the contact with Gibson (NYK) at the start of the drive and loses his balance while attempting the rip-through move.
Kuminga (GSW) makes contact with Fournier's (NYK) back and left arm in an attempt to commit a take foul.
Poole (GSW) commits a take foul on Burks (NYK).
Burks (NYK) commits a take foul on Curry (GSW).
Curry (GSW) commits a take foul on Reddish (NYK).
Poole (GSW) stumbles toward Burks (NYK) off-ball after making foot-to-foot contact with his teammate Lee (GSW), and marginal contact occurs.
